Dialogs.Dialog: What's up with the happy face？
First meeting makes me nervous. Nice to meet you.
Well, I don't want to be too formal.
Um, I'm Rinko Kobayakawa. Nice to meet you.
Not really... is it obvious when I say it？
Rinko's in a pretty good mood today.
Hehe, I feel kind of happy. Rinko is in a pretty good mood today.
It is neither good nor bad.
Who knows？ That is how it is.
You know, I just wanted to ask you something...
Hey, I was thinking about it... but, I'd like to hear it from you.
Yes, like that, that's how it is.
You said you can handle it.
Rinko might think a little differently.
I see. Yeah, that makes some sense.
Hmmm... I wonder if that's true？
There's no way you can answer that.
If you don't want to say it, that's fine.
When you act like that, it makes me want to ask you more and more.
Rinko want to hears it next time.
Ah！ Rinko wants to ask you something.
It's okay, what do you want to talk about？
Oh, I'm not allowed to say that？
So, how are things going these days, boyfriend？
Rinko might not be able to imagine life without him anymore... I don't even want to think about it. Hehe.
When I'm with him, I feel a kind of a pang in my chest. You know what I mean？ It's like a "squeal."
I think Rinko has already broken down. Because all I can think about is him.
> Rinko and him are like one and the same. No one can get in our way... I'd say▼
"We will be together forever"... You don't have to say it, you can see it in your eyes▼
I like him so much, I don't know how to express it any more. He seems to feel the same way, hehe▼
We're actually fighting... I'd like to make up, but it's not going well.
We had a bit of a fight. I'm trying to make up, but it's not going well.
We're fighting... Ah, geez, how did this happen？
Well, maybe a change of scenery would help to be more honest？
I think the other person can probably tell that you want to make up with them.
Let's see, what's it like to be doing skinship with your boyfriend？
Hey, how about skinship？ How do I say it... is it going well？
You know, are you a good kisser, boyfriend？
We feel good... maybe. It makes me happy.
Maybe Rinko's boyfriend is good at it. I'm not proud of it.
Well, I wonder. If you don't know, then maybe you're not good at it.
I feel like it's nothing... I'm not saying I don't like it.
You know... When I want you to have skinship with me, should I appeal to you to do so？
Kissing... we don't do it much, and it's weird.
How's dating going lately？ Are you having fun？
I'm having a lot of fun, taking a detour on my way home from school.
Well, I guess I enjoy a normal date.
I had a very special memory the other day. When I think back on it... Hehe.
Hehe, I went to his house. I was so excited.
You came to my house the other day. I feel like the room looks a little different from what it usually does.
Well, I'm very excited about something. Hehe... won't tell you what it's about.
After school, you know, I just want to hang out with my boyfriend a whole lot more！ If I say that, isn't that stressful？
Don't you think we should stop by your room before going home？
Don't you want to go out at least when there is some special event？
The usual date is nice, but it's not all the time. You want a special date once in a while, don't you？
Wouldn't an after-school date be fun？
It's nice to meet outside, but wouldn't it be nice to have a date at your house？
It's the everyday date that makes the special date stand out. Don't you think？
That's great！ We'll have special memories.
Of course your house is nice, but don't you want to go out together on holidays？
Next time, why don't I invite my boyfriend to my room？
Dating in your own room is nice, but it's nice to go visit your boyfriend's room, isn't it
The thought of my boyfriend being in my room makes me kind of nervous.
After a date, if someone says they want to be with you forever... what would you think？ What would you do？
I know... Rinko might think so too.
Wait, that's... That's because Rinko is also...
Hmm, I may not think that far yet...
What！？ Rinko... doesn't know about that.
Hey, do you ever cook for your boyfriend？
Listen, I'd like to hear about your home-cooking. Of course, I mean cooking for your boyfriend.
Well, I don't do much... I guess I cook breakfast for them a lot.
Yeah, I'm probably going to cook dinner quite a bit.
When we study together at home, I prepare homemade snacks.
After a special date, I'll probably be more enthusiastic about cooking.
Maybe I make more Western food.
That's right... I think I make a lot of Chinese food.
I cook without thinking of the genre.
I'm interested in local cuisine, and I might make it often. It's fun to know the taste of each region.
There's a dish I'm pretty confident about, and I'll give you the recipe so you can make it.
Speaking of cooking, my boyfriend loved the last batch I cooked for him. I'll teach you how to make it, so you can try it too.
Well, thanks. I don't know if I can do it well, but I'll give it a try.
Do you think Rinko can do it？ I'll give it a try.
Really？ I'm glad, that's very helpful.
You know... how do you think I should overcome my weakness in cooking or something like that？
Hey... can you get your boyfriend's tastes right？ It's kind of difficult...
I just wanted to ask you a few questions at... Do you have a large repertoire of cooking？ Rinko doesn't have much...
If that's the case, why don't you try changing the seasonings？ That alone can make it look rather good.
I think you have to do a few first... and then it will come naturally.
It's the things you're not good at that you should make over and over again and practice a lot. I'm sure your boyfriend will understand.
There are different tastes in seasonings. It might be a good idea to find a seasoning that your boyfriend likes.
Why don't you ask your boyfriend for his opinion？ There's no need to be reserved.
Oh, and I'll tell you what Rinko is good at.
Well, I'll tell you one dish I recommend. Try it sometime.
What's it like to eat on a date？
Have you found a nice place to eat for a date night？
That's the thing... I don't go out to eat much.
I often go out to eat with him. I always feel the food tastes better when I eat with him.
We're going out to eat, but I don't think we'll like it too much.
Rinko and him have the same tastes in food, so I can usually leave the restaurant selection to him.
I guess it's mostly conversation during meals. Well, it's fun.
It's fun while we eat. We feed each other, hehe.
We usually end up at the same restaurant. It's okay though, because we both love it.
I go to a rather wide variety of stores. It's more fun that way.
Before I knew it, we'd conquered all the stores in the area, it seems.
There's quite a discrepancy between his favorite food and Rinko's...
When you go on a date, do you take pictures？
Do you take pictures during a date？
When you get your picture taken by your boyfriend, is it normal？ Is that... a service shot or something like that？
Sometimes when you're taking a picture, you're not sure how much to ask for？
He doesn't seem to be very interested in photography...
That guy really likes to take pictures. I'm just happy to have more memories.
He's good at taking photos, but I'm not sure if his skills are up to par yet.
That's the thing, that guy is really good at taking pictures. Where did he practice？
I don't mind that he likes photography, but... the angle is a bit weird. It's not that it's creepy, that's what men are like...
He seemed to be totally addicted to cameras. He had a lot of parts that I didn't understand.
To my surprise, his photo won an award in a contest. Well... the subject was girlfriend, so...
I'm willing to do what he asks. I trust him.
Well... If it makes him happy, I guess I can put up with some of it.
If you get too carried away, I'll kick you.
You don't want to take a bad picture and have it remain in the future. It's for your own good to say no when you have to.
That guy is trying to take naughty pictures of me... Should I get angry？
You have a nice ring on your finger.
You know, I like your hair.
Hehe. Actually, it's a gift from him.
Thanks. Well, I changed the color to suit his taste.
When I want to please my boyfriend, I do my best in many ways. After all, I want him to say I'm cute.
Talking about fashion among girls is stimulating, isn't it？
Hmm... If I had to think about it, I'd say it's going to be a gradual process, right？
That's true. I'm vaguely thinking that it would be nice if we could stay together forever. Geez... the end.
I can't even think about the future. I just want to be with him all the time...
I don't know about the future, but I can say for sure that... Rinko loves him right now and probably will never change that feeling.
I can't help but grin at the thought of the future. I hope he feels the same way.... Rinko is ready to believe and follow him...
When I think about my future with him, I just can't keep my cool. My head is all messed up, but the only thing that's clear to me is that I love him...
There is no future without him in Rinko's mind. That's why I've already made up my mind that we're going to stay together.
I don't know, I just got hyped up today.
I've been thinking a lot about it.
I knew girl talk would never stop.
That's all for this time. Let's talk again.
If we get too carried away, our boyfriends will get jealous. I'll see you next time.
Time's up, time to end this. Let's get lively once again.
Is it that late already？ That's it for today, good night.
